

MODEL DETAILS

This app lets you drag and drop an image of a car, and it will predict what kind of damage it has. The model is trained on third-quarter front and rear views, so the uploaded image should clearly capture either the third-quarter front or rear view of a car.

Used ResNet50 for transfer learning.
The model was trained on around 1,750 images with 6 target classes.

![app](Screenshot 2026-04-20 114103.png)

Classes:

Front Normal
Front Crushed
Front Breakage
Rear Normal
Rear Crushed
Rear Breakage
The accuracy on the validation set was approximately 80%.
SETUP
To get started, first install the dependencies using:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Run the Streamlit app:
streamlit run app/main.py